// Realization is meant to answer this question:  "From the amount that was billed, what amount was actually sent to the clients".
// Staff members enter hours they worked into PCS.  When sending the bills the biller has the ability to either write up or write down those bills.  These are called adjustments.
// Realization represents what precentage of the total billings is the billings after adjustments.
